title Sweep Orphaned Bindings

loop every so often 
  Sweeper->S2: GET /v2/service_bindings
  S2-->Sweeper: <bindings>
  Sweeper->CC: GET /v2/apps
  CC-->Sweeper: <apps>
  Sweeper->Sweeper: filter_orphaned_bindings
  loop orphaned_bindings
    Sweeper->S2: DELETE /v2/service_bindings/:binding_id
    S2->Broker: DELETE /v2/service_instances/:instance_id/service_bindings/:binding_id
    Broker-->S2: 200
    S2->S2: record_audit_event
    S2-->Sweeper: 200
  end
end
